description:
Are you in the mood for some humorous ringtones? You came to right application! The “Funny Human Tricks” application features ringtones of the great comedian Eddie Murphy, memorable Gordon Ramsey phrases of “Hell’s Kitchen”, hilarious lines from “Bruno”, and many more fun tones.

You will have access to the hilarious assortment of “Funny Human Tricks” ringtones that are currently available, PLUS access to additional “Funny Human Tricks” ringtones that we will continue to add on this application in the future.

Warning: Some ringtones contain explicit content. 

NOTE: We highly recommend that you have WiFi or good network connection in order to experience the full functionality of this app.
